rmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/63760/', '', 'Simvastatin, Guar gum, Rosuvastatin', 'Tinidazole, Pantoprazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Metronidazole, Vonoprazan, Amoxicillin, Lansoprazole, More', 1767369485);
