rmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/63771/', '', 'Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Simvastatin, Troglitazone, Rosuvastatin', 'Rifamycin, Kanamycin, Ampicillin, Azithromycin, Acyclovir, Netilmicin, Polymyxin B, Famciclovir, Cefuroxime, Trifluridine, Tobramycin, More', 1767369485);
